@startuml CQRS-Query-Flow
!theme plain

title CQRS 查询时序图 - CQRS Query Sequence

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceStyle arrow
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam noteBorderColor #1565C0

' === Participants ===
actor User as "用户"
participant Dashboard as "Dashboard\n(React)"
participant APIServer as "API Proxy\n(Node.js)"
participant OperatorAgent as "OperatorAgent\n(Python)"
participant OpQueryCtrl as "OperatorQuery\nController"
participant OpQuerySvc as "OperatorQuery\nService"
participant OpRepo as "Operator\nRepository"
participant MySQL as "MySQL\nDatabase"

' === Participants for Parallel Query ===
participant IndQueryCtrl as "IndicatorQuery\nController"
participant IndQuerySvc as "IndicatorQuery\nService"
participant IndRepo as "Indicator\nRepository"

' === Auto-number ===
autonumber 1.1

' === Main Flow ===
User -> Dashboard : 1. 选择运营商\n查看数据看板
activate User
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> APIServer : 2. GET /api/query/operators
Dashboard -> APIServer : 3. GET /api/query/site-cells
Dashboard -> APIServer : 4. GET /api/query/indicators/latest
activate APIServer

' === Parallel Query Execution ===
par
    APIServer -> OpQueryCtrl : 5a. GET /operators
    activate OpQueryCtrl
    OpQueryCtrl -> OpQuerySvc : 6a. findOperators()
    activate OpQuerySvc
    OpQuerySvc -> OpRepo : 7a. SELECT operator_info
    activate OpRepo
    OpRepo -> MySQL : 8a. JDBC Query
    MySQL --> OpRepo : 9a. Operator List
    OpRepo --> OpQuerySvc : 10a. Operator List
    deactivate OpRepo
    OpQuerySvc --> OpQueryCtrl : 11a. Operator List
    deactivate OpQuerySvc
    OpQueryCtrl --> APIServer : 12a. Query Result
    deactivate OpQueryCtrl
also
    APIServer -> OpQueryCtrl : 5b. GET /site-cells
    activate OpQueryCtrl #LightGreen
    OpQueryCtrl -> OpQuerySvc : 6b. findSiteCellSummary()
    activate OpQuerySvc
    OpQuerySvc -> OpRepo : 7b. SELECT site_info
    activate OpRepo
    OpRepo -> MySQL : 8b. JDBC Query
    MySQL --> OpRepo : 9b. Site Summary
    OpRepo --> OpQuerySvc : 10b. Site Summary
    deactivate OpRepo
    OpQuerySvc --> OpQueryCtrl : 11b. Site Summary
    deactivate OpQuerySvc
    OpQueryCtrl --> APIServer : 12b. Query Result
    deactivate OpQueryCtrl
also
    APIServer -> IndQueryCtrl : 5c. GET /indicators/latest
    activate IndQueryCtrl #LightBlue
    IndQueryCtrl -> IndQuerySvc : 6c. findLatestIndicators()
    activate IndQuerySvc
    IndQuerySvc -> IndRepo : 7c. SELECT indicator_info\nWHERE MAX(created_time)
    activate IndRepo
    IndRepo -> MySQL : 8c. JDBC Query
    MySQL --> IndRepo : 9c. Latest Indicators
    IndRepo --> IndQuerySvc : 10c. Latest Indicators
    deactivate IndRepo
    IndQuerySvc --> IndQueryCtrl : 11c. Latest Indicators
    deactivate IndQuerySvc
    IndQueryCtrl --> APIServer : 12c. Query Result
    deactivate IndQueryCtrl
end par

APIServer --> Dashboard : 13. 汇总查询结果
deactivate APIServer

Dashboard -> Dashboard : 14. 渲染看板\n图表 + 表格
Dashboard -> User : 15. 展示数据看板
deactivate Dashboard
deactivate User

' === Notes ===
note over User, MySQL #E8F5E9
  **CQRS Query Side 特点:**
  - 直接从 Repository 读取数据
  - 无需 LLM 调用
  - 优化读取性能
  - 水平扩展查询服务
end note

note over Dashboard
  **并行查询:**
  三个查询并行执行
  asyncio.gather() 收集结果
end note

@enduml